X_1,X_2
 \begin{align} \phi_{X_1}(u_1)&=\int_{\Bbb R}e^{iu_1x_1}dP^{X_1}\\ &=\int_{\Bbb R}e^{iu_1x_1}dP^{X_1}\int_{\Bbb R}dP^{X_2}\\ &=\int_{\Bbb R}\left(\int_{\Bbb R}e^{iu_1x_1}dP^{X_1}\right)dP^{X_2}\\ &=\int_{\Bbb R^2}e^{iu_1x_1}P^{X_1}\otimes P^{X_2} \end{align} 
 P^{(X_1,X_2)}=P^{X_1}\otimes P^{X_2}. 
